I"$<p>The <code>xiaomi_miio</code> device tracker platform is observing your Xiaomi Mi WiFi Repeater 2 and reporting all associated WiFi clients.</p>
<p>Please follow the instructions on <a href="/integrations/vacuum.xiaomi_miio/#retrieving-the-access-token">Retrieving the Access Token</a> to get the API token.</p>
<p>To add a Xiaomi Mi WiFi Repeater device tracker to your installation, add the following to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">device_tracker:
  - platform: xiaomi_miio
    host: 192.168.130.73
    token: YOUR_TOKEN
</code></pre>
